dct_title_s: A plan of the cities of London and Westminster, with the Borough of Southwark
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Border is divided into miles from the meridian and parallel of St. Paul's. Limits of the City are colored red.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published according to Act of Parliament ... by William Faden ... , 20th April 1781.
